## âš ï¸ Important Notes

**Google Sheets Setup:**
- Service account must have Editor access
- Private key must use `\n` for newlines in secrets
- Don't commit credentials to GitHub (in .gitignore)

**Crawling Limits:**
- Default 100 pages max (adjustable)
- Increase for larger sites
- Lower for faster scans

**Status Codes:**
- 200 = OK âœ…
- 404 = Not Found âŒ
